    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained luxury sedan offers a perfect blend of performance and reliability. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, showing only the minor stone chips and light surface scratches expected from careful daily use. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the premium leather seating is supple and free of any rips or significant wear, and the dashboard remains crack-free. All onboard electronics, including the infotainment system, heated seats, and dual-zone climate control, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, featuring a complete service history with a recent oil change and a fresh brake service. The engine runs smoothly, and the transmission shifts seamlessly. With tires that have approximately 70% tread remaining and a clean, non-smoker interior, this vehicle is ready for its next owner to drive away with total confidence.",
